Package: fnos-rescue
Version: 0.1.2
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.11), util-linux, file, btrfs-progs, mdadm, qemu-utils, e2fsprogs, ntfs-3g
Maintainer: FNOS Rescue contributors
Description: Read-only-first FNOS Basic-disk Btrfs recovery toolkit
 FNOS Rescue provides durable cases, safety guards, resumable jobs, validated
 copying, and evidence collection for Linux-based recovery workflows.
